Sample backbone.js and codeigniter application


---------
FRONT END

Final folder contains one file index.html which is implemented using backbone.js , it makes REST API calls to the backend which is implemented using codeigniter

---------
BACK END

backbone folder contains the code for codeigniter.

In application/controller folder, backend.php implements two functions that accepts get and put request.
The model for this is in application/models folder. urls_model.php , which interacts with the database for storing or fetching data.

---------
mysql

backbone.sql conains the database backbone
It has two tables, urls and tags for storing the data.